do you want to come with me?

845
00:51:15,430 --> 00:51:16,252
Can I?

846
00:51:16,750 --> 00:51:17,507
Of course.

847
00:51:18,730 --> 00:51:20,320
If you come with me,

848
00:51:20,350 --> 00:51:23,889
my family will roll out the red carpet to welcome you.

849
00:51:24,380 --> 00:51:25,723
Why do you think so?

850
00:51:26,960 --> 00:51:30,012
Because I don’t really have friends.

851
00:51:30,440 --> 00:51:32,572
When I make new ones,

852
00:51:33,033 --> 00:51:35,030
my parents are really happy.

853
00:51:37,507 --> 00:51:38,812
Just kidding.

854
00:51:41,000 --> 00:51:43,200
I just want to share my home with you.

855
00:51:43,510 --> 00:51:47,304
I just want to find a way to make you smile more,

856
00:51:47,323 --> 00:51:50,984
without wearing Arm’s animal-printed yellow pajamas.

857
00:51:58,510 --> 00:52:00,596
Thank you, Beagle.

858
00:52:04,150 --> 00:52:06,276
You’re welcome, friend.

859
00:52:13,240 --> 00:52:14,289
Our business is doing well.

860
00:52:14,320 --> 00:52:15,329
I just hope we make this much money every day.

861
00:52:15,347 --> 00:52:16,190
Cheers.

862
00:52:23,650 --> 00:52:24,609
Hi, guys.

863
00:52:24,627 --> 00:52:25,236
Hi.

864
00:52:25,261 --> 00:52:26,209
Hi.

865
00:52:27,820 --> 00:52:28,615
Sit here.

866
00:52:31,530 --> 00:52:32,646
