869
00:52:36,440 --> 00:52:37,415
I’m Wa.

870
00:52:37,698 --> 00:52:38,701
That’s Nop.

871
00:52:39,000 --> 00:52:40,467
And that’s Newton,

872
00:52:40,486 --> 00:52:41,347
Yotha’s big brother.

873
00:52:41,360 --> 00:52:42,449
Hi.

874
00:52:42,547 --> 00:52:44,720
Yotha, you brought your friend here.

875
00:52:44,756 --> 00:52:46,356
You should take care of him.

876
00:52:46,381 --> 00:52:48,775
