884
00:53:08,670 --> 00:53:09,310
No.

885
00:53:16,200 --> 00:53:17,403
A cider it is.

886
00:53:18,780 --> 00:53:19,790
What about you, Yotha?

887
00:53:19,821 --> 00:53:20,627
What do you want to drink?

888
00:53:23,310 --> 00:53:24,584
Just water. I drove here.

889
00:53:24,787 --> 00:53:25,427
Okay.

890
00:53:28,380 --> 00:53:31,501
So how’s sharing a room with Yotha?

891
00:53:31,910 --> 00:53:34,203
I bet it’s dead quiet.

892
00:53:34,690 --> 00:53:35,901
Not really, Nop.

893
00:53:37,580 --> 00:53:39,083
