Come on.

904
00:54:02,972 --> 00:54:03,440
Yes.

905
00:54:03,470 --> 00:54:05,144
Count me in.

906
00:54:05,930 --> 00:54:06,960
Cheers!

907
00:54:17,450 --> 00:54:20,763
Gun, have you ever been scared
of anything in your life?

908
00:54:21,260 --> 00:54:22,449
Why do you ask?

909
00:54:22,473 --> 00:54:23,809
Because you’re unusual.

910
00:54:24,067 --> 00:54:25,563
How can you be around Yotha?

911
00:54:25,587 --> 00:54:26,535
Aren’t you scared of him?

912
00:54:29,230 --> 00:54:32,953
